SUMMARY:2026 Study Abroad Fair
DTSTAMP:20260620T130333Z
DTSTART:20260911T160000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Rice Office of Study Abroad welcomes all Rice undergraduate
	 students to our annual Study Abroad Fair! Please join us on Friday\, Sept
	ember 11\, 2026 from 11am to 2pmat Grand Hall (inside the RMC)!  The fair 
	is designed to give students the opportunity to meet face-to-face with our
	 exchange and direct enrollment institutions\, as well as select third-par
	ty provider representatives. In addition to study abroad program represent
	atives\, expect to see a handful of exchange students and study abroad alu
	mni\, who will be there to share their experiences.  All Rice Office of St
	udy Abroad staff members will also be present to share information and ans
	wer questions. Come ask questions and hear about the many study abroad opp
	ortunities that are available through our office!\n\nhttps://events.rice.e
	du/event/430275-2026-study-abroad-fair\n\nFrom Rice University - Open to t
	he Public
URL:https://events.rice.edu/event/430275-2026-study-abroad-fair
GEO:29.7174;-95.4018
LOCATION:Grand Hall
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:rice-public-events
CATEGORIES:Rice University - Open to the Public
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
